<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">أبي عزة قال:</span> سمعته <span class="c2">(نهى)</span> <span class="c2">(٢)</span> عن تجصيص <span class="c2">(القبر)</span> <span class="c2">(٣)</span> <span class="c2">(وقال)</span> <span class="c2">(٤)</span>: لا تجصصوه.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
